Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.47,0:00:45.22,Normal Dialog Text,Steven,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}爽～! 完美钟点午后三明治 达成!\N{\rENG}Yes! Perfectly timed afternoon sandwich complete. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.82,0:00:49.62,Normal Dialog Text,Steven,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等下 我可不能单独吃如此完美的三明治\N{\rENG}Wait, I can't eat such a perfect sandwich all on its own. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.62,0:00:51.08,Normal Dialog Text,Steven,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}得有点配餐\N{\rENG}It needs a side. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.08,0:00:52.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但用什么呢?\N{\rENG}But what? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 嘿 紫晶 我做午餐了\N{\rENG}Oh, hey, Amethyst. I made lunch. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.54,0:00:59.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你想吃空盒子吗?\N{\rENG}You want to eat this empty container? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.56,0:01:00.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 谢了\N{\rENG}No, thanks. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.80,0:01:01.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}O-okay. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.12,0:01:03.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你看到石榴或珍珠了吗?\N{\rENG}You seen Garnet or Pearl? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.28,0:01:04.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没\N{\rENG}Nope. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你猜她们可能在哪?\N{\rENG}Any idea where they might be? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.60,0:01:08.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.70,0:01:10.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}反正不是在相互交谈\N{\rENG}Somewhere not talking to each other. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.14,0:01:11.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Hmm. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯 我知道需要什么了\N{\rENG}Wait, I know what this meal needs. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一袋...\N{\rENG}A bag of...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.88,0:01:18.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}洋葱头?!\N{\rENG}Onion?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.68,0:01:20.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}搞毛?\N{\rENG}What the...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.88,0:01:22.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 不 你可别想\N{\rENG}Oh, no, you don't. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}洋葱头!\N{\rENG}Onion! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们才装上的纱窗!\N{\rENG}We just put that screen in! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}给我回来!\N{\rENG}Come back here! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.64,0:01:32.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那得用来完成我的完美午餐!\N{\rENG}Those were going to complete my perfect lunch! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.98,0:01:35.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可是特别口味啊 \N{\rENG}It's a special flavor
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.02,0:01:37.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}限时供应的!\N{\rENG}that's only in stores for a limited time! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道到你手里的食物的下场!\N{\rENG}I know how you are with food! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你从来都不吃!\N{\rENG}You're not even gonna eat them! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}至少让我尝一口啊!\N{\rENG}At least let me have just one! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.08,0:01:51.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊哈 洋葱头 无处可躲了吧\N{\rENG}This is it, Onion. Nowhere to hide. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.56,0:01:53.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在放-放下零食和-\N{\rENG}Now just--just drop the bag and--
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.26,0:01:55.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...洋葱头?\N{\rENG}uh...Onion? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.58,0:01:57.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...\N{\rENG}Uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.06,0:01:59.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶?\N{\rENG}Amethyst? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...这就有点诡异了!\N{\rENG}Uh...That's really weird! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.34,0:02:11.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 所以...我一直清楚洋葱头有点怪 但...\N{\rENG}Um, so...I always knew Onion was weird, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我感觉他对你有点那啥?\N{\rENG}I think he's obsessed with you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.63,0:02:15.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你觉得呢 紫晶?\N{\rENG}What do you think, Amethyst? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.64,0:02:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁在那里?\N{\rENG}Who's in there? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 我不知道你如何绕过油布的\N{\rENG}Now, I don't know how you got past that tarp, 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这可是私人领地\N{\rENG}but this is private property. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}维达利亚?\N{\rENG}Vidalia?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶?!\N{\rENG}Amethyst?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}都多少年了!\N{\rENG}It's been years! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.48,0:02:29.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}天 你变了好多\N{\rENG}Man, you've changed. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.41,0:02:31.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看起来糟透了!\N{\rENG}You look terrible! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.11,0:02:32.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你还是一样...\N{\rENG}You look the same...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.65,0:02:33.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}遭!\N{\rENG}Terrible! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.12,0:02:36.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等 怎么了?\N{\rENG}Wait, what? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.96,0:02:39.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她是谁? 你们是怎么认识的?\N{\rENG}Who's she? How do you know each other? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 我们都和你爸有交往 \N{\rENG}Oh, we both kind of hung around your dad, 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但维达利亚比你爸更酷 \N{\rENG}but Vidalia's cooler than your dad, 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以我们便开始单独交往了\N{\rENG}so we started hanging out without him. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是史蒂文吧? 看看\N{\rENG}Is that Steven? Look at him. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}长得和格雷格一模一样\N{\rENG}He looks just like Greg. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没什么 没什么 他原来可帅了\N{\rENG}That's good. That's good. He used to be super hot. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.74,0:02:59.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 所以你们原来在一起时画的这些?\N{\rENG}Uh, so did you paint these when you used to hang out? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是啊 应该说是一部分 不过有些是新画的\N{\rENG}Yeah, some of them. Some are new, though. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.34,0:03:04.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶曾是我最喜欢的模特\N{\rENG}Amethyst was my favorite model. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你仍然可以变成任何物体吧?\N{\rENG}Can you still turn into anything? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然 不过正经的不行\N{\rENG}Anything but respectable. 
Dialogue: 600,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.66,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处紫晶的造型致敬毕加索的超现实立体派肖像画
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 天哪 我们之前可惹过各种麻烦\N{\rENG}Oh, man, we used to get into all sorts of trouble. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来告诉我 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Now tell me, Steven, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们算不算叛逆先锋?\N{\rENG}aren't we just the spitting image of mischief? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}勉强把\N{\rENG}Hardly. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么穿拖鞋了\N{\rENG}You're wearing slippers. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你可猜不到我用这双鞋干过什么\N{\rENG}You don't know what I've done in these shoes. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很高兴再次见到你\N{\rENG}It's great to see you again. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起好久没联系了\N{\rENG}Sorry it's been so long. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我猜我们都很忙吧\N{\rENG}I guess we've both been busy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 对啊 我知道-小孩嘛\N{\rENG}Oh, yeah. I get it--kids. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}孩子怎么了?\N{\rENG}What about kids? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 这就有个\N{\rENG}Oh, here's one now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是洋葱头的妈妈?!\N{\rENG}You're Onion's mom?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.14,0:03:43.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错\N{\rENG}Yep. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他就是我的小捣蛋鬼\N{\rENG}He's my little troublemaker. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.88,0:03:48.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且 史蒂文 他很喜欢谈论你\N{\rENG}And, Steven, he loves talking about you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 那是个好主意!\N{\rENG}Oh, that's a great idea! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 紫晶 洋葱头想知道\N{\rENG}Steven, Amethyst, Onion wants to know
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们愿不愿离留下吃晚餐\N{\rENG}if you'd like to stay for dinner. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.08,0:03:58.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃\N{\rENG}Um
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然啦 \N{\rENG}We'd love to, 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对吧 史蒂文? 洋葱头就像 你的好朋友\N{\rENG}Right, Steven? Onion's, like, your best friend. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.57,0:04:05.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在 该告诉我你穿着拖鞋做过什么了吧 妹子?\N{\rENG}Now, tell me what you did in those shoes, girl. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可没法再多塞一口\N{\rENG}Mm, I can't eat another bite of
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那种不可言状的玩意了\N{\rENG}Whatever that was. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 那只是一道\N{\rENG}Oh, it's just a little dish
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我起名为奶油炒面条的菜\N{\rENG}I like to call noodles and butter. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我简直不敢相信过了这么久\N{\rENG}I can't believe how long it's been. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是说 看看他\N{\rENG}I mean, check this guy out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我之前可是比他高的\N{\rENG}I used to be bigger than him. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你之后有臭子马蒂的消息吗?\N{\rENG}Do you ever hear from old farty Marty? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.64,0:04:24.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蛤?\N{\rENG}Hm? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可不知道那个笨蛋在哪\N{\rENG}I don't know where that fool is. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也不在乎\N{\rENG}Don't care, either. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}之后一直是我和黄鳍在一起\N{\rENG}It's just been me and Yellowtail for a while now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊?!\N{\rENG}What?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}黄鳍?\N{\rENG}Yellowtail? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错 我们直接来了电\N{\rENG}Yeah, things just kind of happened. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}之后 我就和渔民在一起了\N{\rENG}Next thing you know, I'm living with a fisherman. 
Dialogue: 50,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.34,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}你该看看你的表情\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}You should see your face right now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 酸奶油\N{\rENG}Hey, Sour Cream. 
Dialogue: 50,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.60,Background Dialogue,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}我怎么猜得到?\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}I just didn't expect any of this. 
Dialogue: 50,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.62,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}好吧 事情现在就是这样\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Well, that's just how it is now. 
Dialogue: 50,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.59,Background Dialogue,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}那么现在老鱼鳍在哪?\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}So where's old fish tail at? 
Dialogue: 50,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.22,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}呃 是"黄鳍"\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Uh, it's Yellowtail. 
Dialogue: 600,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.22,Hint,,0,0,0,,黄鳍用土豆泥做雕像的镜头致敬斯皮尔伯格的电影"第三类接触"中的著名镜头\N其中男主将土豆泥塑造成了自己喜欢的山脉的形状
Dialogue: 50,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.60,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}他大部分时间在海上\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}He spends a lot of time out at sea. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 那是我\N{\rENG}Hey, it's me. 
Dialogue: 50,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.22,Background Dialogue,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}伙计 你之前可一直在抱怨\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}Dude, you used to complain so much
Dialogue: 50,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.56,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}码头的那种味道\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}about the smell at the docks. 
Dialogue: 50,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.64,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}那里原来可恶心了\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}It used to be so gross over there. 
Dialogue: 50,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.90,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}现在那里\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Now there are all these fancy boats hanging around. 
Dialogue: 50,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.52,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}还记得我们曾偷偷进入市长的船然后乱搞一气吗?\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Remember when we snuck on to the mayor's boat and trashed it? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么你这么讨厌食物?\N{\rENG}Why do you hate food? 
Dialogue: 50,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.27,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}对啊 我还记得\N{\rENG_BKG}Yeah, I remember. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你呢 紫晶?\N{\rENG}What about you, Amethyst? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃?\N{\rENG}Huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你一晚上还没说过你的故事呢\N{\rENG}You haven't said a word about yourself all night. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其实 这是因为我的生活太无聊了\N{\rENG}Well, that's because my life is boring. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 宝石人们怎么样?\N{\rENG}All right, how are the gems? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道 她们也很无聊\N{\rENG}I don't know. They're boring, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 谢谢你们的晚安 该走了 不是吗 紫晶?\N{\rENG}Okay, thanks for dinner. Time to go, right, Amethyst? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}急什么集? 我们又没事做\N{\rENG}What's the hurry? We got nothing to do. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}另 紫晶/ 维达利亚派对从不停止\N{\rENG}'Sides, an amethyst/ vidalia party don't end
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}除非太阳出来了\N{\rENG}till the sun come up. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.54,0:05:34.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}妈-妈\N{\rENG}Ma-ma. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.10,0:05:35.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么了?\N{\rENG}What's that? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.76,0:05:38.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}妈妈妈妈-麻麻-嘛-码-码-嘛～\N{\rENG}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 那是个好主意!\N{\rENG}Oh, that's a great idea! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.12,0:05:42.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 洋葱头想带你看看屋子\N{\rENG}Steven, Onion wants to show you around the house. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么样? 让洋葱头带你看看?\N{\rENG}What do you say? Can Onion tote you around? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.10,0:05:52.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃.. 发.. 发生了什么?\N{\rENG}Uh...W-what's going on? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 每当酸奶油开始打碟 \N{\rENG}Oh, whenever Sour Cream starts deejaying, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就会用光整栋房的电力\N{\rENG}it uses all the electricity in the house. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还好黄鳍不在家-\N{\rENG}Good thing Yellowtail's not here--
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这能逼疯他的\N{\rENG}it drives him nuts. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}伙计 你的房子嗨上天了\N{\rENG}Dude, your house is jacked. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能怎么办? 孩子们要表现自我\N{\rENG}What can you do? Kids got to express themselves. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你也是 洋葱头\N{\rENG}You too, Onion. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}相当有表现力\N{\rENG}Very expressive. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看来他准备好了 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Looks like he's ready for you, Steven. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...挺酷的购物车\N{\rENG}Uh...Cool shopping cart. 
Dialogue: 600,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.28,Hint,,0,0,0,,洋葱头床头的海报致敬摇滚乐队The Door
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么你不在蹦床上跳呢?\N{\rENG}Why don't you just jump up and down on that trampoline? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是说 就像 在那\N{\rENG}I mean, it's, like, right there. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这是你的房间...\N{\rENG}But it's your room...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}.. 那么随你便啦\N{\rENG}...So do whatever you want. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你还有个小老鼠做室友!\N{\rENG}You have a little mousy roommate friend! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗷～\N{\rENG}Aww! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.56,0:06:39.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦\N{\rENG}Oh. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是你的宠物?\N{\rENG}Is that your pet? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 他一定住那里 对吧?\N{\rENG}Oh, that must be where he lives, right? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我帮你将他放回家\N{\rENG}Let me help you put him in his home. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这对小宝宝来讲真是个大箱-\N{\rENG}This is a pretty large container for a little baby--
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蛇!\N{\rENG}snake! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}洋葱头, 你想让我Onion, you want me
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}用我们的小伙伴喂蛇吗?\N{\rENG}to feed our little friend to this snake, huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.70,0:07:02.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦\N{\rENG}Oh. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦\N{\rENG}Oh. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起 但我们都得吃饭的\N{\rENG}Sorry, but we all got to eat. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.24,0:07:09.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我...\N{\rENG}I...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}做不到!\N{\rENG}Can't! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃! 赶紧把他从我手里拿走吧!\N{\rENG}Ugh! Just take him from me! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:14.04,0:07:15.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我就在这里\N{\rENG}I-I'll be over here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.98,0:07:19.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...\N{\rENG}Uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不会再给我看更多的奇怪宠物了 对吧?\N{\rENG}You don't have any more weird pets to show me, do you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要放电影?\N{\rENG}You gonna put on a movie? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那真不错-一点也不怪异\N{\rENG}That'd be nice--and not creepy at all. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.06,0:07:30.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}医院布景不错嘛\N{\rENG}Cool hospital setting. 
Dialogue: 50,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.26,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}好的 我准备好了\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Okay, I'm ready. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 那是你妈妈\N{\rENG}Hey, that's your mom. 
Dialogue: 50,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.16,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}我准备好了!\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}I'm ready! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她准备好做什么?\N{\rENG}What's she getting ready for? 
Dialogue: 50,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.18,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}哦\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Oh. 
Dialogue: 50,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.66,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}哦-黄鳍-我觉得...\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Oh, Yellowtail, I think...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.78,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}哦-他要出来了\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Oh, it's happening! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 等下! 发生了什么?!\N{\rENG}Ugh, wait! What's going on?! 
Dialogue: 50,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.96,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}他来了!\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Here he comes! 
Dialogue: 500,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.80,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs128\frz13.72\pos(974,324)\c&H6143B1&\bord0\shad0}生日快乐 洋葱头
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是你出生的视频吗?!\N{\rENG}Is this you being born?! 
Dialogue: 50,0:07:48.48,0:07:51.10,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}哦 我坚持不下去了-\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB9F1FA&}Oh, I am never doing this--
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我没法再承受了\N{\rENG}I can't take much more of this. 
Dialogue: 600,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.41,Hint,,0,0,0,,这个很明显了 "肖申克的救赎"里的越狱隧道
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哪里?\N{\rENG}Where? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.60,0:08:02.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 我得走了\N{\rENG}Okay, I'm out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不能再继续了 得回家了\N{\rENG}Can't do this anymore. Need to go home. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 对不起 但是时候-\N{\rENG}Amethyst, I'm sorry, but it's time to--
Dialogue: 50,0:08:05.52,0:08:06.78,Background Dialogue,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}所有事都一团糟\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}Everything is a mess, 
Dialogue: 50,0:08:07.92,0:08:11.24,Background Dialogue,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}即使是石榴 就像 我从没见过石榴这么生气过\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HD897C1&}even Garnet, like, I've never seen Garnet this upset. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.68,0:08:14.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}家里感觉非常遭 我感觉非常压抑\N{\rENG}It's awful at home. I feel trapped. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那真是太夸张了 不过我知道你的意思\N{\rENG}That's crazy. I know what you mean, though. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.26,0:08:17.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真的?\N{\rENG}You do? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 我们一家并不总是相处的非常愉快\N{\rENG}Hey, we don't always get along in this family. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}黄鳍和酸奶油总是相互掐架\N{\rENG}Yellowtail and Sour Cream are always at each other's throats. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这让我非常苦恼\N{\rENG}It makes me nuts. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}实际上 每当我烦恼时 \N{\rENG}Actually, when I get like that, 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我总想到你\N{\rENG}I think about you
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有你毫不在乎的态度\N{\rENG}and how you could always just roll with it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.97,0:08:31.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?!\N{\rENG}What?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! 就是你\N{\rENG}No! That was you! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你当初是那么...酷\N{\rENG}You were so...Cool. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.44,0:08:39.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就像...一个跟着你的蠢海绵\N{\rENG}I was just like...A dumb sponge following you around. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你 遇事沉着 心无畏惧\N{\rENG}But you were down for anything, not afraid of anything. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道我有多想变成你吗?\N{\rENG}You know how much I wanted to be like you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 我现在仍然这么认为\N{\rENG}Ugh. I still think about it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}说实话 这也是为什么我再次开始画你的画像\N{\rENG}To be honest, that's why I started painting you again. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.54,0:08:53.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我深受你的激励 紫晶\N{\rENG}I'm--I'm inspired by you, Amethyst. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 看来我得再泡一杯茶了\N{\rENG}Oh, looks like I'm gonna need more tea. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你想吃了茶包吗?\N{\rENG}You want to eat this bag? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然啊 这可是最爱\N{\rENG}Yeah, my favorite. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的 我很快就回来\N{\rENG}Okay, I'll be right back. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还好孩子们一直有事情做\N{\rENG}Good thing the kids are keeping themselves busy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 洋葱头 继续吧\N{\rENG}Okay, Onion, let's do this. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}无论你准备了多么怪异或恐怖的东西 \N{\rENG}Whatever weird or horrible thing you have planned for me, 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.81,0:09:13.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我都能接住\N{\rENG}I can take it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 慢点\N{\rENG}Hey, slow down. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.38,0:09:27.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 天哪 这可不会有什么好结果\N{\rENG}Oh, boy. This is gonna be bad. 
Dialogue: 600,0:09:24.38,0:09:27.34,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处画面的移动方式与周边游戏Attack the Light相同
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 呃 洋葱头 你在哪?\N{\rENG}Uh, uh, Onion, where are you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是什么房间?\N{\rENG}What's this room? 
Dialogue: 600,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.42,Hint,,0,0,0,,洋葱头的秘密房间与位置是皮克斯总部内部酒吧的再现
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦!\N{\rENG}Oh! 
Dialogue: 600,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.08,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处洋葱头的画像致敬"2001太空漫游"中的星孩
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里有什么? 可怕的东西吗?\N{\rENG}What's in there? Something horrible? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}洋葱头! 箱子里全是侠盗玩偶!\N{\rENG}Onion! It's full of guys! 
Dialogue: 600,0:09:47.36,0:09:48.24,Hint,,0,0,0,,红色的忍者侠盗致敬洛克人2中的Quickman
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔～\N{\rENG}Wow! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我从没见过红色的忍者侠盗啊\N{\rENG}I've never seen this red variant of ninja guy before. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你还有女侠?!\N{\rENG}You have gals, too?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}安全帽女侠!\N{\rENG}Hard hat gal! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}三角女侠!\N{\rENG}Triangle gal! 
Dialogue: 600,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.40,Hint,,0,0,0,,粉色三角为同性恋同性恋斗争的标志
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橘子女侠!\N{\rENG}Orange gal! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}凯伦!\N{\rENG}Karen! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.24,0:09:59.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}凯伦...\N{\rENG}Karen...
Dialogue: 600,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.82,Hint,,0,0,0,,看起来像不像Rebecca Sugar( 糖姐)? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是怎么收集到-不 别告诉我\N{\rENG}How'd you get a hold of--no, don't tell me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.20,0:10:03.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯?\N{\rENG}Hmm? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不可能吧!\N{\rENG}No way! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是探险女侠!\N{\rENG}It's explorer gal! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她看起来可酷了!\N{\rENG}She's so cool-looking! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢你让我看看她-\N{\rENG}Thanks for showing her to me--
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你-你应该收回你的探险女侠\N{\rENG}you--you should take your explorer gal back. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.08,0:10:19.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是要送给我吗?\N{\rENG}Are you giving this to me? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我简直不敢相信!\N{\rENG}I can't believe it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}太感谢你了 洋葱头!\N{\rENG}Thank you so much, Onion! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗷 天哪! 你还有什么侠盗和女侠?!\N{\rENG}Aw, man! What other gals and guys you got?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈 太酷了-隐身侠盗\N{\rENG}Ha, cool--invisible guy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们可以走啦\N{\rENG}And stay out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 谢谢你们的晚餐-和倾听\N{\rENG}Um, thanks for dinner--and for listening. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然 也谢谢你们闯进我家\N{\rENG}Well, thanks for breaking into my house. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}同时不要担心那件事\N{\rENG}And don't worry about that other stuff. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.80,0:10:41.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那迟早会过去的\N{\rENG}It's gonna blow over. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是块石头\N{\rENG}You're a rock. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不是吗?\N{\rENG}That's what you are, right? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 差不多吧\N{\rENG}Uh, something like that. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 不论你是什么 一定不要见外啊\N{\rENG}Well, whatever you are, don't be a stranger. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.96,0:10:53.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然 我随时可以来 只要你需要-\N{\rENG}Yeah, I can stop by anytime if you need, 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.52,0:10:54.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}灵感\N{\rENG}inspiration. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:55.64,0:10:56.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或者如果你需要 \N{\rENG}Or if you want, 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你也可以偶尔来神庙看看\N{\rENG}you could come over to the temple sometime, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你也可以带上洋葱头来和史蒂文玩\N{\rENG}You could even bring Onion for Steven to hang with. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 当然 这听起来不错\N{\rENG}Oh, well, that sounds great to us. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你呢 史蒂文?\N{\rENG}What about you, Steven? 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你准备好和他再来一局吗?\N{\rENG}You ready for another round with this guy? 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然啦 改天见\N{\rENG}Yeah, we'll see. 
